# Zona14: added in this fork
ent-STWeaponRifleOC14939 = OTs-14 "Groza" 9x39
  .desc = An assault-rifle/grenade-launcher complex chambered in its native 9 × 39mm caliber.

ent-STWeaponRifleOC14Liturgia = OTs-14M "Liturgia"
  .desc = An OTs-14 Groza modified within the Zone — a rare specimen chambered for the 7.62×39 cartridge widely available in the Exclusion Zone. The weapon's polymer parts are a dark brown color resembling Bakelite, but in fact aren't, and have no precise composition. Most likely they are an anomalous substance synthesized within the Zone. It has an integrated suppressor with a tactical foregrip, a collimator sight of unknown origin, and a charm in the shape of a mutant fang. Such weapons are wielded by the Firstborn Seraphim.
